{"timestamp":"2026-05-27T01:55:24.788092Z","level":"info","event":"Done. Returned value was: [{'q': 'Whether you have a problem in your life or not depends upon your own attitude, your own understanding.', 'a': 'Shunryu Suzuki', 'c': 102, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Whether you have a problem in your life or not depends upon your own attitude, your own understanding.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Shunryu Suzuki</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Don't seek, don't avoid, don't expect. Take what comes and be happy.\", 'a': 'Maxime Lagace', 'c': 68, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Don&#039;t seek, don&#039;t avoid, don&#039;t expect. Take what comes and be happy.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Maxime Lagace</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Fashion fades, only style remains the same.', 'a': 'Coco Chanel', 'c': 43, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Fashion fades, only style remains the same.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Coco Chanel</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'No matter how great the talent or efforts, some things just take time.', 'a': 'Warren Buffett', 'c': 70, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;No matter how great the talent or efforts, some things just take time.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Warren Buffett</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Your heart is the size of an ocean. Go find yourself in its hidden depths.', 'a': 'Rumi', 'c': 74, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Your heart is the size of an ocean. Go find yourself in its hidden depths.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Rumi</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"What we learn from history is that people don't learn from history.\", 'a': 'Warren Buffett', 'c': 67, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;What we learn from history is that people don&#039;t learn from history.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Warren Buffett</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'A man who cannot tolerate small misfortunes can never accomplish great things.', 'a': 'Chinese Proverb', 'c': 78, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;A man who cannot tolerate small misfortunes can never accomplish great things.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Chinese Proverb</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'We will outstretch the hand if you unclench your fist.', 'a': 'Barack Obama', 'c': 54, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;We will outstretch the hand if you unclench your fist.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Barack Obama</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Do not go where the path may lead, go instead where there is no path and leave a trail.', 'a': 'Ralph Waldo Emerson', 'c': 87, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Do not go where the path may lead, go instead where there is no path and leave a trail.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Ralph Waldo Emerson</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The energy of the mind is the essence of life.', 'a': 'Aristotle', 'c': 46, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The energy of the mind is the essence of life.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Aristotle</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Success comes to those who become success conscious.', 'a': 'Napoleon Hill', 'c': 52, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Success comes to those who become success conscious.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Napoleon Hill</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'When you are tough on yourself, life is going to be infinitely easier on you.', 'a': 'Zig Ziglar', 'c': 77, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;When you are tough on yourself, life is going to be infinitely easier on you.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Zig Ziglar</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Never be afraid to raise your voice for honesty and truth and compassion against injustice and lying and greed.', 'a': 'William Faulkner', 'c': 111, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Never be afraid to raise your voice for honesty and truth and compassion against injustice and lying and greed.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>William Faulkner</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'You cannot find peace avoiding life.', 'a': 'Virginia Woolf', 'c': 36, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;You cannot find peace avoiding life.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Virginia Woolf</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Fear of death is fear of the Unknown.', 'a': 'Adi Da Samraj', 'c': 37, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Fear of death is fear of the Unknown.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Adi Da Samraj</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Success does not consist in never making mistakes but in never making the same one a second time.', 'a': 'George Bernard Shaw', 'c': 97, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Success does not consist in never making mistakes but in never making the same one a second time.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>George Bernard Shaw</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Thinking is the hardest work there is. That is why so few people engage in it.', 'a': 'Robert Kiyosaki', 'c': 78, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Thinking is the hardest work there is. That is why so few people engage in it.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Robert Kiyosaki</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Our joy does not have to be based on our circumstances.', 'a': 'Joyce Meyer', 'c': 55, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Our joy does not have to be based on our circumstances.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Joyce Meyer</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Optimism is the one quality more associated with success and happiness than any other.', 'a': 'Brian Tracy', 'c': 86, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Optimism is the one quality more associated with success and happiness than any other.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Brian Tracy</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Stop being tormented by everyone else's reaction to you.\", 'a': 'Joyce Meyer', 'c': 56, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Stop being tormented by everyone else&#039;s reaction to you.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Joyce Meyer</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"If you realize that you're the problem, then you can change yourself, learn something and grow wiser. Don't blame other people for your problems.\", 'a': 'Robert Kiyosaki', 'c': 145, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;If you realize that you&#039;re the problem, then you can change yourself, learn something and grow wiser. Don&#039;t blame other people for your problems.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Robert Kiyosaki</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The future depends on what you do today.', 'a': 'Mahatma Gandhi', 'c': 40, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The future depends on what you do today.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Mahatma Gandhi</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'What lies behind us and what lies before us are tiny matters compared to what lies within us.', 'a': 'Ralph Waldo Emerson', 'c': 93, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;What lies behind us and what lies before us are tiny matters compared to what lies within us.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Ralph Waldo Emerson</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The more something threatens your identity, the more you will avoid it.', 'a': 'Mark Manson', 'c': 71, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The more something threatens your identity, the more you will avoid it.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Mark Manson</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'You have the potential for greatness.', 'a': 'Steve Harvey', 'c': 37, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;You have the potential for greatness.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Steve Harvey</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Expect the best of yourself, and then do what is necessary to make it a reality.', 'a': 'Ralph Marston', 'c': 80, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Expect the best of yourself, and then do what is necessary to make it a reality.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Ralph Marston</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'You need a plan to build a house. To build a life, it is even more important to have a plan or goal.', 'a': 'Zig Ziglar', 'c': 100, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;You need a plan to build a house. To build a life, it is even more important to have a plan or goal.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Zig Ziglar</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The only reason to be alive is to enjoy it.', 'a': 'Rita Mae Brown', 'c': 43, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The only reason to be alive is to enjoy it.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Rita Mae Brown</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Don't put off living to next week, next month, next year or next decade. The only time you're ever living is in this moment.\", 'a': 'Celestine Chua', 'c': 124, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Don&#039;t put off living to next week, next month, next year or next decade. The only time you&#039;re ever living is in this moment.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Celestine Chua</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'We are all faced with a series of great opportunities brilliantly disguised as impossible situations.', 'a': 'Charles Swindoll', 'c': 101, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;We are all faced with a series of great opportunities brilliantly disguised as impossible situations.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Charles Swindoll</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Keep your eyes on the goal, and just keep taking the next step towards completing it.', 'a': 'John Carmack', 'c': 85, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Keep your eyes on the goal, and just keep taking the next step towards completing it.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>John Carmack</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Never lose hope. Storms make people stronger and never last forever.', 'a': 'Roy T. Bennett', 'c': 68, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Never lose hope. Storms make people stronger and never last forever.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Roy T. Bennett</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Don't be pushed by your problems; be led by your dreams.\", 'a': 'Unknown', 'c': 56, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Don&#039;t be pushed by your problems; be led by your dreams.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Unknown</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Don't be afraid to stand for what you believe in, even if that means standing alone.\", 'a': 'Unknown', 'c': 84, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Don&#039;t be afraid to stand for what you believe in, even if that means standing alone.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Unknown</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'One reason so few of us achieve what we truly want is that we never direct our focus; we never concentrate our power.', 'a': 'Tony Robbins', 'c': 117, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;One reason so few of us achieve what we truly want is that we never direct our focus; we never concentrate our power.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Tony Robbins</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"If you're afraid to die, you're afraid to live. You can't have one without the other.\", 'a': 'Rita Mae Brown', 'c': 85, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;If you&#039;re afraid to die, you&#039;re afraid to live. You can&#039;t have one without the other.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Rita Mae Brown</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"The more rejection you get, the better you are, the more you've learned, the closer you are to your outcome.\", 'a': 'Tony Robbins', 'c': 108, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The more rejection you get, the better you are, the more you&#039;ve learned, the closer you are to your outcome.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Tony Robbins</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Always keep your eyes open. Keep watching. Because whatever you see can inspire you.', 'a': 'Grace Coddington', 'c': 84, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Always keep your eyes open. Keep watching. Because whatever you see can inspire you.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Grace Coddington</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"I don't walk away from things that I think are unfinished.\", 'a': 'Arnold Schwarzenegger', 'c': 58, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;I don&#039;t walk away from things that I think are unfinished.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Arnold Schwarzenegger</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'A hut full of laughter is richer than a palace full of sadness.', 'a': 'Zen Proverb', 'c': 63, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;A hut full of laughter is richer than a palace full of sadness.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Zen Proverb</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'If we are honest with ourselves, most of us will have to admit that we live out our lives in an ocean of fear.', 'a': 'Jon Kabat-Zinn', 'c': 110, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;If we are honest with ourselves, most of us will have to admit that we live out our lives in an ocean of fear.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Jon Kabat-Zinn</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'The highest level of wisdom is when you not only accept but love adversity.', 'a': 'Maxime Lagace', 'c': 75, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;The highest level of wisdom is when you not only accept but love adversity.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Maxime Lagace</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Appear weak when you are strong, and strong when you are weak.', 'a': 'Sun Tzu', 'c': 62, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Appear weak when you are strong, and strong when you are weak.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Sun Tzu</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Living life in style also means living a life of balance.', 'a': 'Jim Rohn', 'c': 57, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Living life in style also means living a life of balance.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Jim Rohn</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Try not to become a man of success, but rather try to become a man of value.', 'a': 'Albert Einstein', 'c': 76, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Try not to become a man of success, but rather try to become a man of value.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Albert Einstein</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'One of the first signs of the beginning of understanding is the wish to die.', 'a': 'Franz Kafka', 'c': 76, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;One of the first signs of the beginning of understanding is the wish to die.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Franz Kafka</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'Your life does not get better by chance, it gets better by change.', 'a': 'Jim Rohn', 'c': 66, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Your life does not get better by chance, it gets better by change.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Jim Rohn</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': \"Be happy in the moment, that's enough. Each moment is all we need, not more.\", 'a': 'Mother Teresa', 'c': 76, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;Be happy in the moment, that&#039;s enough. Each moment is all we need, not more.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Mother Teresa</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'To live is to be willing to die over and over again.', 'a': 'Pema Chodron', 'c': 52, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;To live is to be willing to die over and over again.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Pema Chodron</footer></blockquote>'}, {'q': 'No one ever is defeated until defeat has been accepted as a reality.', 'a': 'Napoleon Hill', 'c': 68, 'h': '<blockquote>&ldquo;No one ever is defeated until defeat has been accepted as a reality.&rdquo; &mdash; <footer>Napoleon Hill</footer></blockquote>'}]","logger":"airflow.task.operators.airflow.sdk.definitions.asset.decorators._AssetMainOperator","filename":"python.py","lineno":229}
